      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NUKKUNYA (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.35) at this track behind MATT JET POWER in a NG. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Can go on with it. ICE ON FIRE (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Dinali Keroma (22.49) in a Grade 4/5. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Expecting another good run. MATT JET POWER (3) recorded a win over the 388m at this track in a swift 22.30 last start. In form and must include in calculations. RUBY JUAN (4) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
